<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freund, als ir uns
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Conczen Krebs, ewrs
                <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s,</expan> und Andres im Hofs,
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den
                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> Andres im Hof,
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan> für uns besant und <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> czu
            rede gesaczt. Der hat uns geantwurtt, wie im der
              <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>onczen</ex></expan> Krebsz ein guldein gelihen hab, den hab er
                <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>m</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> wider geschickt und <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> als
            er des <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> bekentlich sey. Und von des pferds
                <expan>wege<ex>n,</ex></expan> daz im derselb ewr <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>
            auch gelihen sull <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, spricht der
                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan> daz er im <add>kein pferd</add> nicht gelihen, sunder
                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fraw<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, der künigin, diener gelihen hab; doch wie
                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> deucht den <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>onczen</ex></expan> Krebsz, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er,</ex></expan> daz er darüber czu dem
              <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Andres im Hof, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan> icht <expan>cze spreche<ex>n</ex></expan> het,
                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> slewnigs
                <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen hie vor des reichs richter bey uns czu
                <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des
                <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so derselb <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist, <expan>on gev<ex>er</ex>d</expan>;
                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Mich<ex>aelis.</ex></expan>
</ab>
